70: - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n1071: resources:\n1072: - agentruntimes\n1073: - codeinterpreters\n1074: verbs:\n1075: - get\n1076: - list\n1077: - watch\n1078: - create\n1079: - update\n1080: - patch\n1081: - delete\n1082: \n1083: apiGroups:\n1084: - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n1085: resources:\n1086: - agentruntimes/status\n1087: - codeinterpreters/status\n1088: verbs:\n1089: - get\n1090: - update\n1091: - patch\n1092: \n1093: apiGroups:\n1094: - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n1095: resources:\n1096: - codeinterpreters/finalizers\n1097: verbs:\n1098: - update\n1099: ```\n1100: \n1101: ## Version Migration Strategy\n1102: \n1103: Future migration path from v1alpha1 to v1beta1/v1:\n1104: \n1105: 1. Create new version package `pkg/apis/runtime/v1beta1/`\n1106: 2. Implement conversion functions between v1alpha1 and v1beta1\n1107: 3. Update CRD to serve both versions (v1alpha1 and v1beta1)\n1108: 4. Set v1beta1 as storage version\n1109: 5. Update controllers and clients to use v1beta1\n1110: 6. Deprecate v1alpha1 after migration period\n1111: \n1112: ```go\n1113: // pkg/apis/runtime/conversion.go\n1114: package runtime\n1115: \n1116: import (\n1117:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n1118:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1beta1\"\n1119:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/conversion\"\n1120: )\n1121: \n1122: func (src *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime) ConvertTo(dstRaw conversion.Hub) error {\n1123:     dst := dstRaw.(*v1beta1.AgentRuntime)\n1124:     // Conversion logic\n1125:     return nil\n1126: }\n1127: \n1128: func (dst *v1beta1.AgentRuntime) ConvertFrom(srcRaw conversion.Hub) error {\n1129:     src := srcRaw.(*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n1130:     // Conversion logic\n1131:     return nil\n1132: }\n1133: ```\n1134: \n1135: ## Dependencies\n1136: \n1137: ### Go Dependencies\n1138: \n1139: ```go\n1140: import (\n1141:     metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n1142:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n1143:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n1144:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/intstr\"\n1145: )\n1146: ```\n1147: \n1148: ### Build Tools\n1149: \n1150: - `controller-gen`: v0.17.2 (for CRD and deepcopy generation)\n1151: - `k8s.io/code-generator`: v0.34.1 (for client-go generation)\n1152: \n1153: ### Makefile Targets\n1154: \n1155: | Target | Description |\n1156: |--------|-------------|\n1157: | `gen-crd` | Generate CRD manifests |\n1158: | `gen-client` | Generate client-go library |\n1159: | `generate` | Generate all code (CRD + deepcopy + go mod tidy) |\n1160: | `gen-all` | `generate` + `gen-client` |\n1161: | `gen-check` | Verify generated code is up-to-date |\n1162: \n1163: ## Documentation\n1164: \n1165: ### API Reference\n1166: \n1167: Auto-generated from CRD OpenAPIV3Schema:\n1168: - `AgentRuntime` spec and status fields\n1169: - `CodeInterpreter` spec and status fields\n1170: - Validation rules and constraints\n1171: \n1172: ### Client-Go Documentation\n1173: \n1174: Auto-generated from source code:\n1175: - Interface definitions\n1176: - Method signatures\n1177: - Usage examples\n1178: \n1179: ### Examples\n1180: \n1181: **AgentRuntime example** (`examples/agentruntime.yaml`):\n1182: \n1183: ```yaml\n1184: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n1185: kind: AgentRuntime\n1186: metadata:\n1187:   name: python-agent\n1188:   namespace: agentcube\n1189: spec:\n1190:   maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n1191:   sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n1192:   targetPort:\n1193:   - port: 8080\n1194:     protocol: \"HTTP\"\n1195:     pathPrefix: \"/api\"\n1196:   podTemplate:\n1197:     metadata:\n1198:       labels:\n1199:         app: python-agent\n1200:     spec:\n1201:       containers:\n1202:       - name: agent\n1203:         image: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/python-agent:latest\n1204:         resources:\n1205:           limits:\n1206:             cpu: \"500m\"\n1207:             memory: \"512Mi\"\n1208:           requests:\n1209:             cpu: \"100m\"\n1210:             memory: \"128Mi\"\n1211: ```\n1212: \n1213: **CodeInterpreter example** (`examples/codeinterpreter.yaml`):\n1214: \n1215: ```yaml\n1216: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n1217: kind: CodeInterpreter\n1218: metadata:\n1219:   name: python-interpreter\n1220:   namespace: agentcube\n1221: spec:\n1222:   authMode: \"picod\"\n1223:   maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n1224:   sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n1225:   ports:\n1226:   - port: 8080\n1227:     protocol: \"HTTP\"\n1228:   template:\n1229:     spec:\n1230:       containers:\n1231:       - name: interpreter\n1232:         image: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/python-interpreter:latest\n1233:         resources:\n1234:           limits:\n1235:             cpu: \"1\"\n1236:             memory: \"1Gi\"\n1237:           requests:\n1238:             cpu: \"250m\"\n1239:             memory: \"256Mi\"\n1240:     warmPoolSize: 2\n1241: ```\n\n(End of file - total 1241 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# pkg/apis — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition Design\n\n## AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n**Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRDs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go generation, and provide type-safe API access.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n├── runtime/\n│   └── v1alpha1/\n│       ├── agentruntime_types.go   # AgentRuntime spec/status\n│       ├── codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter spec/status\n│       ├── doc.go                   # Package documentation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md","time":{"start":1775883289581,"end":1775883289606}}}}
