\"CodeInterpreter\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go && echo \"DeepCopy methods generated\" || echo \"Generation failed\"\n226: ```\n227: \n228: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n229: - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` file exists\n230: - Contains `DeepCopy()` methods for CodeInterpreter\n231: - Contains `DeepCopyInto()` methods for CodeInterpreter\n232: - Contains `DeepCopyObject()` methods implementing `runtime.Object`\n233: - Contains DeepCopy methods for CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList\n234: - No compilation errors in generated code\n235: \n236: ---\n237: \n238: ### [ ] TASK-010: Test DeepCopy methods for CodeInterpreter\n239: **Description**: Write and run tests to verify DeepCopy methods work correctly for CodeInterpreter.\n240: \n241: **Test File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n242: \n243: **Test Cases**:\n244: - Test `DeepCopy()` creates independent copies of CodeInterpreter\n245: - Test modifications to copy don't affect original\n246: - Test CodeInterpreterSpec is deep copied\n247: - Test CodeInterpreterStatus is deep copied\n248: - Test CodeInterpreterList is deep copied\n249: - Test slice fields (Env, EnabledPackages) are deep copied\n250: \n251: **Verification**:\n252: ```bash\n253: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy -v\n254: ```\n255: \n256: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n257: - All DeepCopy tests for CodeInterpreter pass\n258: - Copies are independent from originals\n259: - No shared references between original and copy\n260: - Nested structs are properly deep copied\n261: \n262: ---\n263: \n264: ### [ ] TASK-011: Generate CRD YAML manifests\n265: **Description**: Run controller-gen to generate CRD YAML files including CodeInterpreter.\n266: \n267: **Command**:\n268: ```bash\n269: controller-gen crd paths=\"./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\" output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds\n270: ```\n271: \n272: **Verification**:\n273: ```bash\n274: test -f manifests/charts/base/c